Required build tool:
	GCC
	GNU Make

Supported targets:
GNU/Linux:
	linux (>=2.6.28)
	glibc (>2.2)
GNU/Hurd:
	hurd (>=0.5)
	glibc
FreeBSD:
	freebsd (>=10)
Mac OS X:
	osx (>=10.4)
Interix (SFU/SUA):
	interix (>=3.5)
Windows:
	msvcrt (>=6)
	linkcore
Windows CE:
	ceos (>=3.0)
	celibc (>=1.8)
Windows NT:
	ntos (>=3.51)
	nativelibc (>=1.0) (a full set of the Windows NT Native Tools is required)

Depended library:
	libcrypto (>=0.9.7) (included in OpenSSL)

Optional library:
	libselinux (if building with selinux support for GNU/Linux)

Run 'make help' for more information.
